Question: Are all the people the same gender?

Reference Answer: no

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='people')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What is the gender of the person?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What is the gender of the person?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What is the gender of the person?')
ANSWER3=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == {ANSWER1} and {ANSWER0} == {ANSWER2} else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER3)
```
